      <!-- ORDERS & SHIPPING --> 
      <h2>Orders &amp; Shipping</h2>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>Where are you located?</p>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>We're a proudly Canadian shop located in Vancouver, 
            British Columbia <i class="fa-brands fa-canadian-maple-leaf"></i></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>What payment methods do you accept?</p>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>We accept all of the payment methods below, so it's easy to pay however you like!</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Visa (credit and debit cards)</li>
            <li>MasterCard (credit and debit cards)</li>
            <li>American Express</li>
            <li>PayPal</li>
            <li>Apple Pay</li>
            <li>Google Pay</li>
            <li>Afterpay</li>
          </ul>
      </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>Can I cancel my order?</p>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>If you need to cancel your order, contact us as quickly as possible. We work hard to 
            get your items shipped as quickly as possible, so we may be unable to cancel your order 
            after 24 hours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>When will my order arrive?</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Because our jewelry is handcrafted, kindly allow 3 to 5 business days for your items to 
            be made. Once shipped, you will receive an email with your tracking number. Transit times 
            vary depending on location and the selected shipping method-check our shipping options 
            LINKLINKLINK for estimated delivery times.</p>
          <p>Please note that shipping transit times do not include the time it takes to make your item. 
            Be sure to take both production time and transit time into account when ordering!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>Where do you ship?</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>We ship worldwide (but note that exceptions may occur depending on current 
            Canada Post or USPS restrictions).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>Will I be charged import duties or VAT?</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Orders shipped to Canada or the US will not incur import duties or taxes upon 
            delivery. International orders may be assessed customs fees or VAT at the time 
            of entry. Please understand that we are not responsible for these charges, and 
            they are the customer's responsibility to pay. Rates vary by country check with 
            your customs office for specific rates.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- RETURNS & EXCHANGES -->
      <h2>Returns &amp; Exchanges</h2>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>Do you accept returns?</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>IYes! Free returns are accepted within 30 days for Canadian &amp; US orders. 
            International customers may also return items within 30 days, but the customer 
            is responsible for the cost of return shipping. All returned items should be in 
            their unworn original condition and include the packaging. Kindly note that 
            original shipping fees are nonrefundable. START RETURN BUTTON LINK</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>Can I exchange my item?</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Yes! Free exchanges are accepted within 30 days for all Canadian &amp; US orders. 
            International customers may also exchange items within 30 days, but the customer is 
            responsible for the cost of both return shipping and re-shipping. START EXCHANGE BUTTON LINK</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>When will I receive my refund?</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Refunds are processed once we receive your return. Your original payment method will 
            be credited. Note that it may take a few business days for the refund to show in your 
            account.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- WARRANTY & REPAIRS -->
      <h2>Warranty &amp; Repairs</h2>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>Our 6-Month Free Repair Warranty</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>We are happy to offer free repairs for broken items purchased within the last 
            6 months. Orders placed between 6 months and 1 year ago are still eligible for 
            repair, but there may be other associated costs (such as shipping or custom stones/metals).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>How do I request a repair?</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>It's easy! Just fill out our repair form and upload a photo of your broken item. 
            Your replacement piece will be ready within 5 to 7 business days (excluding shipping time).
            START REPAIR BUTTON LINK.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- CUSTOM REQUESTS -->
      <h2>Custom Requests</h2>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>Can you engrave custom constellations or other designs?</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>IAbsolutely! We love collaborating with our clients on custom designs. Since we 
            engrave everything in our own studio, we can accommodate most custom requests. 
            There are some design limitations, such as the size of a jewelry item or the complexity 
            of a design-but we'll guide you through all that stuff. Just reach out with your idea 
            to start! START CUSTOM REQUEST BUTTON LINK</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- SIZING GUIDE -->
      <h2>Sizing Guide</h2>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>How do I find my ring size?</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Order an adjustable ring sizer RING SIZER LINK or use one of the options below 
            to find your ring size.</p>
          <p>OPTION 1: MEASURE YOUR RING</p>
          <p>If you have a ring that already fits your finger perfectly, measure the inner 
            diameter (mm) of the ring on a ruler. Use the chart below to find your ring size.</p>
          <p>OPTION 2: MEASURE YOUR FINGER</p>
          <p>Wrap a strip of paper snugly around your finger. Mark the overlap with a pen, then 
            lay the paper flat against a ruler to measure (mm). Use the chart below to find your 
            ring size.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
